Dear {!Contact.FirstName},

Thank you again for purchasing a multi-user subscription to Compliance Week. Your invoice is attached.

As the internal administrator of {!Account.Name}’s account, you are able to add new users and delete old ones from your account; update contact information for the account users and yourself; and subscribe or remove users from email distribution lists. If there is someone else in your company who handles the maintenance of your subscription, please let us know and we can change the designated administrator on the account.

To change a user's account, follow these steps:

Log on to Compliance Week as normal;
Click on My CW
Select the “Subscription Admin" tab;
Click update user profile of the user account you wish to edit;
Change the desired fields (note, asterisked fields are required);
Click the Update Details button.

Please be aware that your account's user limit is {!Account.User_Limit__c}. If you wish to add additional users, please contact us via phone at (888) 519-9200 or via email.

